title: Elon Musk says Tesla ending Models S and X production, converting Fremont factory lines to make Optimus robots
summary_full: On Tesla's fourth-quarter earnings call, CEO Elon Musk said the company is ending production of its Model S and X vehicles.
summary_public: On Tesla's fourth-quarter earnings call, CEO Elon Musk said the company is ending production of its Model S and X vehicles.
